metadata.name: A Glance Of The Abyss
metadata.description:
A glance of the abyss is  
inquisitiveness of aliens 
or maybe not knowing. 

We can't see what's out there  
we just feel safety from god.

I've never seen a god  
but i've heard its tongue...

The language that requires no words  
but only the power of empathy. 
It shines a light on old perspective  
while giving birth to new dialogue. 

Here is the universe and all  
of it's mysteries I will never  
be able to get answers for.

maybe I don't need them.
